  "c": "KIT & CLASS MODS",
  "n": "Multiclass Kits",
  "no": "Multiclass Kits by Argent77. Generates true multiclass kit combinations from ALL single-class kits installed at time of installation. True multiclass kits don't count against the engine's hardcoded kit limit. Install AFTER all other kit mods (AK, TnB, M&G, FnP, etc.) and BEFORE Talents of Faerun. 'All combinations' can be exponentially slow with many kits installed; 'Choose manually' or 'List kits only' recommended. Arcane multiclass kits may inherit specialist traits due to hardcoded engine behavior.",
  "cl": [
    {
      "d": "2026-03-12",
      "m": "Added from research; v1.1 released 2025-10-24"
    }
  ],
